        public static <T> T[] insert(T[] array,
                             T item)
        Finds the first null value in an array and inserts the new value there. If no values are null, the array is lengthened by 1 and the value is appended to the array.
        Parameters:
        array - The array to insert into
        item - The value to insert
        Returns:
